      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Fought, Failed, Fired Up",
        "Client": "Warrior in Training",
        "Description": "*sigh* I took on a Diablos and failed...\r\nI took on an Anjanath\u2014failed. I just\r\ncan\u0027t anymore. How can it even be\r\ndone? You\u0027ve challenged all sorts\r\nof beasts, surely these are nothing\r\nto you. Maybe if I watch you defeat\r\nthem, it\u0027ll rekindle the fire inside me.",
        "Target": "Hunt a Diablos and an Anjanath",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "D\u00E9fis perdus",
        "Client": "Guerrier en formation",
        "Description": "*soupir* J\u0027ai \u00E9chou\u00E9 face \u00E0 un\r\nDiablos... Face \u00E0 un Anjanath...\r\nS\u00E9rieux, je sature. Comment les\r\ngens font pour r\u00E9ussir \u00E0 vaincre un\r\nmonstre ? T\u0027en as affront\u00E9 un paquet\r\ndes comme \u00E7a, toi. Peut-\u00EAtre que tu\r\npourrais m\u0027inspirer...",
        "Target": "Chasser un Diablos et un Anjanath",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Combatti, fallisci e riprova",
        "Client": "Guerriero in addestramento",
        "Description": "Sob, ho affrontato un Diablos\r\ne ho fallito. Stesso esito con\r\nun Anjanath. Non ne posso pi\u00F9!\r\nCom\u0027\u00E8 possibile? Hai sfidato\r\ntante bestie, questo \u00E8 niente\r\nper te. Forse mi dar\u00E0 coraggio\r\nse ti guardo annientarli.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Diablos e un Anjanath",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Bek\u00E4mpft, besiegt, befeuert",
        "Client": "Krieger-Lehrling",
        "Description": "*seufz* Von einem Diablos besiegt...\r\nVon einem Anjanath... besiegt...\r\nIch kann nicht mehr. Wie geht das\r\n\u00FCberhaupt? Du hast alle m\u00F6glichen\r\nBestien bek\u00E4mpft, die beiden sind\r\nf\u00FCr dich doch ein Witz. Wenn du sie\r\nbesiegst, motiviert mich das sicher.",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Diablos und einen Anjanath.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Luch\u00E9, perd\u00ED, me cabre\u00E9",
        "Client": "Guerrero en ciernes",
        "Description": "He desafiado a un Diablos y un\r\nAnjanath... y he fracasado.\r\nNo puedo ni verlos de nuevo.\r\n\u00BFPodr\u00EDa alguien vencer a uno\r\nde cada para probar que es\r\nposible y devolverme la\r\nesperanza?",
        "Target": "Caza un Diablos y un Anjanath",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041D\u0435\u0443\u0434\u0430\u0447\u0430 \u2014 \u0435\u0449\u0435 \u043D\u0435 \u043A\u043E\u043D\u0435\u0446",
        "Client": "\u0422\u0440\u0435\u043D\u0438\u0440\u0443\u044E\u0449\u0438\u0439\u0441\u044F \u0432\u043E\u0438\u043D",
